      <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">Bathroom</span>
      <p class="text-primary font-semibold mt-1 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors leading-snug">Seattle Bathroom Tile Trends 2026</p>
    </a>
